Package org.apache.commons.rdf.jena.impl

Class JenaFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.rdf.jena.impl.JenaFactory

  • public class JenaFactory
extends Object
    Construct Jena implementations of Commons RDF.

    This class is primarily an internal helper class, users should instead use JenaRDFTermFactory.

    For the purpose of blank node identity, some of these methods require a UUID to use as a salt. See BlankNode.uniqueReference() for details.
